values:
Odd happenings this fine weekend.&nbsp; Visited the Mashantucket Pequot museum on Saturday for the second time.&nbsp; Depressing as always, parts were, when one sees how wonderfully those considered "savages" were treated.&nbsp; On the plus side, they seem to be doing well today.&nbsp; Foxwoods appears to be undergoing some kind of freakishly huge expansion.&nbsp; Even the museum is seeing a boost, with a rather tall observation tower being constructed adjacent to it.&nbsp; 

Odder still, Sunday saw a visit to Mystic Aquarium.&nbsp; Barking sea lions, some beluga whales, assorted other creatures, and a peculiar little XD Motion Theater rounded out the day.

All in all, a strange weekend.&nbsp; 'Course, 'tis all par for the course 'round here.&nbsp; Lookie, three pre-apostrophe'd words in that last sentence. =P
